# GSD planning artifacts; local-only at the source repo root. The pattern is
# root-anchored so it does NOT match nested `.planning/` directories under
# `shared/extras/<logical>/` in the sync-repo mirror (Phase 19 extras-sync
# would otherwise silently fail at the git-add boundary).
